dialog.body: Hello, thank you for contacting Old Stone Auto Insurance. My name is Larry Miller. May I have your name, please?
Hello, Larry. My name is Teresa Brown.
Nice to meet you, Teresa. Could you kindly provide me with your policy number and date of birth for verification purposes?
Sure, my policy number is five six eight two one and my date of birth is December thirtieth, nineteen eighty-five.
Thank you, Teresa. One more thing I need from you is your mailing address. Could you please share that with me?
Of course. My mailing address is one two three Willow Street, Springfield, State, zip code one zero zero two zero.
Thank you for providing the information, Teresa. Is there anything else I can assist you with today?
That's all for now, Larry. Thank you for your help.
You're welcome, Teresa. If you have any more questions in the future, feel free to contact us. Have a great day!
